# CUDRT: Benchmarking the Detection of Human vs. Large Language Models Generated Texts
Zhen TaoZhiyu LiDinghao XiWei Xu\\orgdivSchool of Information,\\orgnameRenmin University of China,\\orgaddress\\stateBeijing,\\countryChina\\orgnameInstitute for Advanced Algorithms Research,\\orgaddress\\stateShanghai,\\countryChina\\orgdivDepartment of Digital Economics,\\orgnameShanghai University of Finance and Economics,\\orgaddress\\stateShanghai,\\countryChina[xidinghao@mail.shufe.edu.cn](mailto:xidinghao@mail.shufe.edu.cn)
